          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "How Does Quality Shape Your Shipping Approach?",
            "faq_des": "<p>At Fleuriation, we believe in slowing down to create something beautiful. Every product is handcrafted in small, intentional batches to ensure freshness, potency, and care in every jar, bottle, and container. Due to this handcrafted approach, our timelines for shipping are designed with both quality and your satisfaction in mind.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_HkAKmW": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What is your Processing Time?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Each order is prepared with care and typically ships within 1–3 business days. During restocks, new launches, or high-demand seasons, processing may take up to 3–5 business days as we create fresh batches just for you.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_rQweNi": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What are your Shipping Methods and Rates?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We ship using trusted carriers (USPS, UPS, or FedEx) to ensure your products arrive safely. Shipping rates are calculated at checkout based on your order and location. Free shipping is available on orders <strong>$75 or more within the United States.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_kL9sMx": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What are your Delivery Timeframes?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Standard shipping generally takes 3–7 business days after processing. Expedited shipping options are available at checkout for faster delivery.</p><p>Please note that these shipping timeframes apply to the United States. International orders may require additional time in transit due to customs processing and regional postal timelines.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_tP2qZa": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Do you use Eco-Friendly Packaging?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We believe in caring for the Earth as much as we care for your body. Orders are packaged using eco-conscious materials whenever possible, from recyclable boxes to compostable fillers, so your unboxing is as gentle on the planet as it is on you. <strong>Please remember to recycle materials and containers after use.</strong></p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Bv7nYd": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Do you offer Order Tracking?",
            "faq_des": "<p>Yes. Once your order ships, you'll receive an email with a tracking number so you can follow its journey from our facility to your doorstep.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Qm5xKe": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "Do you provide International Shipping?",
            "faq_des": "<p>We currently ship to the United States and Canada and are working on adding more international countries. Please note that international customers are responsible for any customs duties, taxes, or other applicable international fees.</p>"
          }
        },
        "faq_Wr4pLn": {
          "type": "faq",
          "settings": {
            "faq_title": "What do you mean by Transparency and Fresh-Batch Promise?",
            "faq_des": "<p>As a small-batch brand, some items may require extra time if they sell out quickly. Should there be any unexpected delays, we'll keep you updated because transparency is part of our promise. Email our customer care team at <a href=\"mailto:support@fleuriation.com\">support@fleuriation.com</a> for more shipping information.</p>"
